column1: 1,1.18650340,"SELECT F.path, RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight FROM FOLDER F

column2: LEFT JOIN FOLDERNAME FN ON FN.name = F.name
LEFT JOIN RATIOBASIS RB ON FN.ratiobasisID = RB.ID
ORDER BY ISNULL(RB.ratio) asc, RB.weight desc"

column1: 2,2.10758860,"SELECT F.name, F.folder, RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight FROM FILE F

column2: LEFT JOIN FILENAME FN ON F.name = FN.name
LEFT JOIN RATIOBASIS RB ON FN.ratiobasisID = RB.ID
ORDER BY ISNULL(RB.ratio) asc, RB.weight desc"

column1: 3,2.59371120,"SELECT F.name, F.folder, RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight FROM FILE F

column2: LEFT JOIN FOLDER FO ON F.folderID = FO.ID
LEFT JOIN FOLDERNAME FN ON FN.name = FO.name
LEFT JOIN RATIOBASIS RB ON FN.ratiobasisID = RB.ID
ORDER BY ISNULL(RB.ratio) asc, RB.weight desc"

column1: 4,2.33041530,"SELECT F.name, F.folder, F.filetype, FT.fileending as 'IDENTIFIED FILEENDING',  RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight FROM FILE F

column2: LEFT JOIN FILETYPE FT ON F.filetype = FT.fileending
LEFT JOIN RATIOBASIS RB ON FT.ratiobasisID = RB.ID
ORDER BY ISNULL(RB.ratio) asc, RB.weight desc"

column1: 5,15.70392640,"SELECT F.name, F.folder, F.sizeInBytes, F.sizeAsString, S.sizeInBytes as 'treshhold sizeInBytes', S.sizeAsString as 'treshhold sizeAsString', RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight

column2: LEFT JOIN SIZE S ON F.sizeInBytes <= S.sizeInBytes
LEFT JOIN RATIOBASIS RB ON S.ratiobasisID = RB.ID

column1: SELECT F.name, F.folder, F.lastAccessedTSD, DATEDIFF(NOW(), F.lastAccessedTSD) as differenceToToday, min(D.days) as minDays FROM FILE F

column3: LEFT JOIN date D on D.lastAccess = 1 and DATEDIFF(NOW(), F.lastAccessedTSD) <= D.days

column1: 9,12.01755260,"SELECT filedata.folder, filedata.name, filedata.lastAccessedTSD, fileData.differenceToToday, D.days as 'treshhold days', RB.recommendedAction, RB.ratio, RB.weight from date D
JOIN fileDataWithMinDaysReference fileData on D.days = fileData.minDays and D.lastAccess = 1
LEFT JOIN ratiobasis rb on D.rat"
